dct_description_sm: Map shows populated areas, shantytowns, roads, cemeteries, wadi, and notable features. Includes location map index showing boundary and glossary. "Map information as of 1992." "A lane is considered as being a minimum of 2.5 meters in width. Normal railroad gauge is 1.44 meters (4ʹ8.5ʹʹ)." "This sheet falls within NC 39-1, 1501, 1:250,000 and NC 39-27, 1:100,000." "Printed by DMAHTC 12-92." "DMA stock no. Y921XBOOSAASO." ©1992
